# UI Design System вЂ” Design Tokens

## Visual Identity
Dark-themed AI SaaS. Tone: modern, powerful, premium.
- Near-black background with purple tint
- Violet/purple as primary brand color
- Glassmorphism cards with subtle border
- Purple/pink mesh gradient on hero sections
- Soft glow effects behind key elements

---

## Token Definition вЂ” `src/styles/global.css`

Tailwind v4 `@theme` registers tokens as **utility classes** automatically.
Use `@theme` for solid colors, radius, and shadows.
Use `:root` for rgba values and gradients (cannot go in `@theme`).

```css
@import 'tailwindcss';
@import '@heroui/styles';

@theme {
  /* в”Ђв”Ђ Backgrounds в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
   * bg-base        в†’ page background
   * bg-surface     в†’ card, panel
   * bg-elevated    в†’ modal, dropdown, tooltip            */
  --color-base:     #09080f;
  --color-surface:  #120f1e;
  --color-elevated: #1c1830;

  /* в”Ђв”Ђ Brand (violet/purple) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
   * bg-brand / text-brand / border-brand
   * text-brand-light / border-brand-light
   * bg-brand-dim                                         */
  --color-brand:       #8b5cf6;
  --color-brand-light: #a78bfa;
  --color-brand-dim:   #6d28d9;

  /* в”Ђв”Ђ Accent (pink/magenta вЂ” hero gradient only) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
   * text-accent / text-accent-light                      */
  --color-accent:       #c026d3;
  --color-accent-light: #e879f9;

  /* в”Ђв”Ђ Text в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
   * text-foreground  в†’ headings, labels
   * text-muted       в†’ body, descriptions
   * text-subtle      в†’ placeholders, hints
   * text-inverse     в†’ text on brand backgrounds         */
  --color-foreground: #ffffff;
  --color-muted:      #a1a1b5;
  --color-subtle:     #6b6b80;
  --color-inverse:    #09080f;

  /* в”Ђв”Ђ Status в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
   * text-success / bg-success  etc.                      */
  --color-success: #22c55e;
  --color-warning: #f59e0b;
  --color-error:   #ef4444;
  --color-info:    #3b82f6;

  /* в”Ђв”Ђ Border Radius в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
   * rounded-card / rounded-pill / rounded-ui-sm etc.     */
  --radius-ui-sm:  6px;
  --radius-ui-md:  10px;
  --radius-card:   16px;
  --radius-ui-xl:  24px;
  --radius-pill:   9999px;

  /* в”Ђв”Ђ Shadows в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
   * shadow-card / shadow-cta                             */
  --shadow-card: 0 4px 24px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.4);
  --shadow-cta:  0 0 20px rgb(139 92 246 / 0.5);
}

/* rgba and gradient values вЂ” cannot live in @theme */
:root {
  --color-brand-glow:    rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.35);
  --color-bg-overlay:    rgba(18, 15, 30, 0.85);

  --gradient-hero:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(192, 38, 211, 0.4) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 75% 40%, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.5) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2) 0%, transparent 50%);
  --gradient-cta:   linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #c026d3 100%);
  --gradient-brand: linear-gradient(135deg, #6d28d9 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #c026d3 100%);
  --gradient-text:  linear-gradient(90deg, #a78bfa, #e879f9);

  --shadow-brand: 0 0 30px var(--color-brand-glow);
}
```

