## Component Patterns

### Page background
```tsx
<div className="min-h-screen bg-base">
```

### Hero section (with mesh gradient backdrop)
```tsx
<section className="relative overflow-hidden bg-base py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div className="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" style={{ background: 'var(--gradient-hero)' }} />
  <div className="relative z-10">{/* content */}</div>
</section>
```

### Glass card
```tsx
<div className="rounded-card border border-brand/20 bg-surface p-6 shadow-card">
```

### Glass card with glow (featured)
```tsx
<div
  className="rounded-card border border-brand/45 bg-surface p-6 shadow-card"
  style={{ boxShadow: 'var(--shadow-card), var(--shadow-brand)' }}
>
```

### CTA button (when NOT using HeroUI Button)
```tsx
<button
  className="rounded-pill px-6 py-2.5 font-semibold text-foreground shadow-cta transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
  style={{ background: 'var(--gradient-cta)' }}
>
```

### Navbar
```tsx
<nav
  className="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/6 backdrop-blur-md"
  style={{ background: 'rgba(9,8,15,0.75)' }}
>
```

### Section heading
```tsx
<h2 className="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-5xl">
  <span className="text-brand-light">AI</span> Image Enhancement
</h2>
<p className="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">...</p>
```

### Brand pill badge
```tsx
<span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-pill border border-brand/45 bg-brand/15 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-brand-light">
  New feature
</span>
```

---

## Typography
- Headings: `font-bold` / `font-extrabold`, `tracking-tight`, `text-foreground`
- Body text: `text-muted` вЂ” never smaller than `text-sm`
- Hints / meta: `text-subtle`

## Spacing & Layout
- Content max-width: `max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- Section padding: `py-20 sm:py-28`
- Card grid: `grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`

## Rules
- **Always use Tailwind classes** (`bg-surface`, `text-muted`, `border-brand/20`, `rounded-card`)
- Only fall back to `style={{ }}` for gradients, glow shadows, and rgba overlays
- Never hardcode hex values anywhere in JSX
- No bare `text-white` or `text-black` вЂ” use `text-foreground` or `text-inverse`
- Glow effects (`shadow-brand`, `shadow-cta`) only on CTA buttons and featured cards
